item.title: [HBASE-12858] Remove unneeded files under src/main/docbkx
item.description:
From https://builds.apache.org/job/PreCommit-HBASE-Build/12463/artifact/patchprocess/patchReleaseAuditProblems.txt :


 !????? src/main/asciidoc/hbase.css

 !????? src/main/docbkx/hbase-default.xml

Lines that start with ????? in the release audit report indicate files that do not have an Apache license header.
